The travis script is hiding the result status of the test executables:

```
    cmake -G "Unix Makefiles" -DASSIMP_ENABLE_BOOST_WORKAROUND=YES -DASSIMP_NO_EXPORT=$TRAVIS_NO_EXPORT -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=$SHARED_BUILD ;
    make ;
    sudo make install ;
    sudo ldconfig ;
    cd test/unit ;
    ../../bin/unit ;
    cd ../regression ;
    chmod 755 run.py ;
    ./run.py ;
    chmod 755 result_checker.py ;
    ./result_checker.py;
```

If `../../bin/unit` fails, the travis build doesn't fail.
